name: 2021 The 4th International Conference on Electrical Engineering and Green Energy（CEEGE 2021）
content: Conference Proceedings： Accepted and presented papers will be published into one of the following: 1) Energy Reports (ISSN: 2352-4847; CiteScore: 4.13; Impact Factor: 3.595) 2) E3S Web of Conference (ISSN: 2267-1242) Proceedings will be online and submit for SCIE, Scopus and EI Compendex index.
